{"search_data": "CentralNew Schemes to Replace Diesel Pump Sets with Solar Pumps SoonSolar Pumps to Replace Diesel Pump SetsThe scheme for solarisation of grid connected solar pump is a good initiative of the central government because at the time of low rainfall, farmers face higher input costs into diesel water pumps. The solarisation of grid connected solar pump will help in agriculture field where power is erratic or not available. Moreover, this scheme will also help in reducing the dependency on diesel fuel.As per the released noticed, the government would focus on improvement of transmission and distribution infrastructure. The power ministry will also monitor the quality of distribution infrastructure and fix accountability at the ground level that would ensure last mile coverage of each beneficiary.Recently, the consultative committee met in Guwahati to review the functioning of National Hydroelectric Power Corporation (NHPC). The committee emphasized on the implementation of the solar rooftop and solar pump programme.However, this scheme has not been officially launched yet, as soon as this scheme is launched, we will update it here.SOURCE: http://www.thestatesman.com/business/scheme-replace-diesel-pump-sets-solar-pumps-soon-1502520562.html  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}